-- Berkshire’s MiTek Building Supply Unit Buys Benson Industries
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2013-07-31T13:39:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-31/berkshire-s-mitek-building-supply-unit-buys-benson-industries.html
MiTek Industries, a building supply
unit of  Warren Buffett ’s Berkshire Hathaway Inc., bought closely
held Benson Industries LLC to expand its offerings to the global
high-rise commercial building market.  Benson designs, manufactures and installs customized
curtain wall systems for hotels, residential, government and
institutional buildings, the unit of Omaha, Nebraska-based
Berkshire said today in a statement distributed by Business Wire
that didn’t disclose terms of the deal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  